Steps Required to install Examserv 
====================================

1. Start the Mysql server
	service mysqld start
2. Start the Apache server
	service httpd start
3. check the status of MySQL and Apache
        service mysqld status
        service httpd status 
4. Untar the Examserver.tar.gz in /var/www/html (default)
   or in document root of Apache server  
        cd /var/www/html
        ls -l ExamServer.tar.gz
        tar -xvzf Examserver.tar.gz
5. Install the database from the command line 
        php examserver_install.php

 Output:Examserv Installation Success !

6. Start and Enjoy the Examserver from the browser
    http://localhost/Examserver

7. hostname can be configured other than localhost.
   The user must configure manually in
   examserver_global.php
   examserver_install.sh 

8. Login with "admin" as user name and "admin" as password
   for administrator

Please feel free to contact ! If you have any troubles in Installing.

Cheer
Shankar Palaniappan  
